casebody.data:
Celeste G. BROUGHTON
v.
COUNTY COMMISSION OF WAKE COUNTY. No. 262P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 12, 2006. Celeste G. Broughton, Pro Se. Shelley Eason, Raleigh, for County Commission of Wake Co.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 12th day of May 2006 for Writ of Supersedeas of the judgment of the Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 12th day of May 2006."
